1. Execute "mst start" from any host in the fabric
2. Execute "mst ib add"
3. Execute "mst status" to identify the switch device name
4. Execute "flint -d <device name> q" to identify the firmware version
 
The "mst" and "flint" commands are part of the Mellanox Firmware Tools (MFT)

ibdev2netdev -v
